<!---

File		: PopUpDocumentThumbNail.mxml
Module		: Video Editing
Developer(s): Vimal Mahendran, Sreelekshmi, Ashish Pillai
Reviewer(s)	: Remya T

File contains the UI for popping up the document details. Pop up contains a image of document, document name
and page number.Pop up happens on the mouse over of document block.

-->
<!-- Main Canvas -->
<mx:Canvas xmlns:mx="http://www.adobe.com/2006/mxml"
		   width="140" height="180" backgroundColor="#FFFFFF" horizontalScrollPolicy="off"
		   verticalScrollPolicy="off">
	<mx:VBox width="100%" height="100%" horizontalAlign="center" horizontalCenter="0" verticalGap="1">
		<mx:Label id="lblDocumentName" height="20" fontSize="10"/>
		<!-- Image for displaying the document image Screen shot -->
		<mx:Image id="imgSlideThumb" maxWidth="140" maxHeight="140"/>
		<!-- Label for displaying the document page number -->
		<mx:Label id="lblPageNo" height="20" fontSize="10"/>
	</mx:VBox>
</mx:Canvas>
